{"tid":56284,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"一人一段最撚塞既行人路","createTime":"2016-12-27T06:23:33.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-27T08:06:30.000Z","uid":12973,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"419286d6fb90bce44f7c429fbfaaff126192dd92","tid":56284,"uid":12973,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T06:23:33.000Z","msg":"有時唔止塞車煩，趕時間既時候行路爬唔到頭都好撚燥<br />\n<br />\n先總結3大原因條路會塞<br />\n1. 路窄，前面個阿婆妹下就影響後面<br />\n2. 多人停低（波鞋街花園街既人成日停低望鋪頭）<br />\n3. 上樓梯/電梯前一段路：大多數人都會收慢上去，變相條龍一長，仲係平路既你都要收油<br />\n<br />\n我先，淘大去得寶一段<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3177a9392950788a6addaa23e20dffef83035018","tid":56284,"uid":62754,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T06:24:40.000Z","msg":"上水所有嘅路<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/21.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"634db282515bbbb3ccea179467dd77d6c4b60b0d","tid":56284,"uid":40354,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T06:28:20.000Z","msg":"元朗大馬路<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"001952698b457e65d9f60e459e08381e229417e1","tid":56284,"uid":25753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T06:30:59.000Z","msg":"沙田新城市入面走廊"},{"pid":"2ea9559df841e2be0348b8aa50e7f51e40584c7b","tid":56284,"uid":12973,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T06:34:55.000Z","msg":"樓上既路全部都中過伏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n上水藥房<br />\n元朗啲人等馬路等到塞死哂<br />\n新城市啲喼"},{"pid":"07bea8b4b40690c96a131cb08ee1da0c0e62f28c","tid":56284,"uid":16756,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T06:39:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>元朗大馬路<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/norm